	keywords = {Agriculture; Air Pollutants; Manure; Methane; Nitrogen; Oryza; Secale; Secale cereale; Biomass; Cellulose; Crops; Cultivation; Fertilizers; Gas emissions; Greenhouse gases; Harvesting; Lignin; Manures; Methane; Nutrients; Organic carbon; Soils; cellulose; lignin; methane; nitrogen; organic carbon; oxide; phosphorus pentoxide; potassium oxide; unclassified drug; air pollutant; manure; methane; nitrogen; Biomass productivity; Chemical compositions; Cover crops; Flooded conditions; Methane production; Plant maturation; Rice cultivation; Secale cerealis; cover crop; green manuring; greenhouse gas; harvesting; methane; nutrient; organic carbon; paddy farming; rice; Article; biomass; carbon footprint; chemical composition; cover crop; dry weight; flooding; flowering; harvesting; manure; nonhuman; nutrient; paddy soil; plant development; plant growth; priority journal; protein content; rye; soil; soil quality; temperature; tillage; agriculture; air pollutant; analysis; Oryza; procedures; Productivity},
